<style>
    .page-medical-review {
        padding: 80px 0;
        background-image: url({{ "page-medical-review.png" | asset_url }});
        background-position: center top;
        background-size: cover;
    }

    .page-medical-review__info {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 840px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 80px 0 0;
    }

    .page-medical-review__info svg {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
    }

    .page-medical-review__info path {
        fill: var(--primary5);
    }

    .page-medical-review__block {
        margin: 8px 0 0;
    }

    .page-medical-review__block > *:not(:last-child) {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
    }

    .page-medical-review__title {
        color: var(--primary5);
    }
</style>

<section class="page-medical-review">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="page-medical-review__info">
            {% render "icon-quote" %}

            <p><b>The final results from the IRB-approved study demonstrated that</b></p>

            <div class="page-medical-review__block">
                <h3 class="h3-title page-medical-review__title">
                    Patients who used Kailo over a period of 30 days showed a vast reduction of their pain severity levels.
                </h3>

                <p>
                    They also experienced a better quality of life, improved function, were very satisfied with the Kailo Pain Patch, and preferred the patch over oral pain medications.
                </p>

                <p>
                    "With the increased focus on identifying alternative therapies for patients experiencing pain, the use and ongoing research of novel approaches including the non-drug and microtechnology based Kailo patch, seem to have a very positive effect on patients who are experiencing mild, moderate, and chronic pain.‚Äù
                </p>

                <p><b>Jeffrey Gudin, MD | Principal Investigator</b></p>

                <a class="button button--primary" href="#">read medical opinons</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
